    • Method Detail

      • lookup

        public static java.lang.String lookup(java.lang.String uuid,
                                      java.lang.String defaultName)
        Uses the internal lookup table to get the description of a given UUID. Child classes need to implement their own lookup method to update their UUID table. However, they can call this method.
        Parameters:
        uuid - The UUID to look up.
        defaultName - The default name if no entry could be found.
        Returns:
        The description of the UUID or the default name if no entry could be found.
